I would hunt in UP if I were you.  There are some nice free upgrades in armor from the raldukans there.  A decent shoulder piece drops there as well but Kiyallmane is correct, the Draconic Pauldrons would be better for you.  Odds are you may get more Kael dropped/Thurg quested armor while you are building faction.  Maybe looking into a Bracer of Benevolance quest would be another free option as well.<br>
<br>
Other than that,  I would also hunt in Maidens eye until I got a Va Shir Claw earring.  Not a huge upgrade in any of this but they are free.  I would also pick up an Axergoths (sp) Belt of Defense there as well in case you can upgrade to a better haste item in another slot.  They rot quite a bit from my exp so it just takes up a bank space.<br>
<br>
Hopefully your guild will be able to tackle HoT soon.  The Myrmidom's armor you could quest from there is quite good and I think would be an upgrade in about any slot but your helmet.  As far as weapons, I don't know.  I have always struggled with this as well because I have always been a poor warrior.<br>
<br>
One final thought may be to get two or three groups from your guild and go into Dragon Necropolis.  There are some decent ratio weapons that drop down in the rat tunnels.  They don't have stats or procs but they aren't too bad.  I have a 10/18 1hs from there.<br>
